abhi 12th january 2014 ko to iss dramay kaa last episode # 281 aya tha phir itni jaldi sirf 6 weeks kay baad season 2 start kernay ki kiya zaroorat thi . aadhi se zyada cast pehlay hi chor ker jaa chuki thi shroo kay 20 , 25 episodes kay baad . baqi bachay khuchay actors bhi kam hoagaye hain ab . laddan ko dubai bhej ker ghaib kerdiya . pinki & chambeli ko maar diya . shakira ko india bhej ker ghaib kerdiya . jannat ki talaq kay baad kam ko bhi bhaga diya . season 2 main iss dramay ko soap bana ker dikaya jaa raha hai lekin pehlay teeno episodes bilkul hi boring hain . soap banany ki bhi koi tuk nahin thi . wesay bhi script naam ki koi cheez nahin hai . bholay ki new heroin bohot thaki hui hai . jannat sahiba pehlay to maree jaa rahi theen bholay kay ishq main lekin ab kam se talaq lenay kay baad jannat ki bholay kay liye mohabbat achanak hi kaheen ghaib hogye hai . teeno boring episodes ko forward kerkay 15 mainutes main dekha hai . lagta hai kay aik din achanak saud & javeria ko khayal aya kay iss ka season 2 shroo kertay hain , usi din saaray bachay kuchay actors ko lekar , baghair kisi script kay recording shroo kerdi aur 3 episodes bana liye . script - less drama , nothing new , nothing exciting .... very boring !!!!!!!
